The last step to get our images to display from Stripe is to update the `next.config.js` file with a parameter to allow us to retrieve the images from stripe.com.

5d33bf5d-fcd3-4037-bde5-f94dbe1516bd.text:
config.js` file with a parameter to allow us to retrieve the images from stripe.com.We can do this by adding the following:

```js
module.exports = {
  reactStrictMode: true,
  // Add this to allow images to be retrieved from stripe.com
  images: {
    domains: ["files.stripe.com"],
  },
